  (text "10. USB 3.1 hub — VL817 (4-port, 5 Gbps / Gen1).  CM5 USB3 port#0 upstream" (at 15 15.0 0) (effects (font (size 1.5 1.5)) (justify left bottom)) (uuid 6b4fc06c-153e-4dd8-82f7-b55411a188fd))
  (text "-> 4x USB-C downstream (J40..J43, SuperSpeed).  RP2354B is OFF-hub (CM5 USB3" (at 15 19.0 0) (effects (font (size 1.5 1.5)) (justify left bottom)) (uuid c1dacbaa-69d1-4d21-9ae0-f7982e817a00))
  (text "port#1 via SW1).  J11 backpack = CM5 USB2 port.  SS TX pairs have AC caps;" (at 15 23.0 0) (effects (font (size 1.5 1.5)) (justify left bottom)) (uuid 5c98e9ee-99bd-452f-80aa-9f0d399803a1))
  (text "USB-C ports are HOST/DFP -> CC Rp pull-ups; per-port VBUS PTC from +5V." (at 15 27.0 0) (effects (font (size 1.5 1.5)) (justify left bottom)) (uuid b0e68f43-3cb7-4c81-a09a-85207029aa07))
  (text "NOTE: one SS lane wired (TX1/RX1) -> USB3 in one C orientation; full flip" (at 15 31.0 0) (effects (font (size 1.5 1.5)) (justify left bottom)) (uuid 16d4f88b-0199-4e07-8b78-99b9f9eb5116))
  (text "needs a per-port 2:1 SS mux (DNP option).  USB2 D+/- works both ways." (at 15 35.0 0) (effects (font (size 1.5 1.5)) (justify left bottom)) (uuid 0ee77bef-4062-408c-a04e-a0d6ea13d4f3))
